{"tid":103400,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解成日一天黑就好多雲","createTime":"2017-02-01T10:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T14:40:09.000Z","uid":78022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e63c79c720a5a464d0e9697d3102288730273242","tid":103400,"uid":78022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:11:49.000Z","msg":"好多時明明日頭好猛太陽得幾舊薄雲<br />\n但一到就黑個陣就變到好多雲<br />\n搞到成日想上山睇星都唔敢去<br />\n有無天文地理撚可以解答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe440c7f485c843e6946c1a7cf1755887312c006","tid":103400,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"月球引力<br />\n原理好似潮漲潮退<br />\n所以天黑好多雲<br />\n利申：鳩up"},{"pid":"7dc51d6db6cb5d8e71107c70220c5aedc0a129b2","tid":103400,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:18:49.000Z","msg":"改變磁通量"},{"pid":"24ebcd0e8750fe955b8b95851f7423625853695c","tid":103400,"uid":78022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:32:42.000Z","msg":"邊個巴打係舊雲入面返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以借一借"},{"pid":"ae0ab3cd57c18367b3dc8a027968d3938d472b73","tid":103400,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:30:18.000Z","msg":"雲量應該同晝夜無直接關係"},{"pid":"1bfd2696de372a085a00e9558e3d0da7455cc05b","tid":103400,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"唯一可能有點相關既係<br />\n日頭時日照令地面升溫, 空氣上升, 產生對流, 水氣積聚成雲至一定程度, 到黃昏至晚上有可能形成雷雨, 呢個係春夏較常見既現象. 當然大氣狀況遠較我地想像複雜唔知幾多倍, 而多雲有雨既現象又會由其他諸多因素導致 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 9up / 我係咪認真左?"}]}